item.description: From November, 25 to 27, 2016 the third Robotic Hamburg Open Workshop (RoHOW) → will be held at the Hamburg University of Technology (TUHH). The RoHOW is an educational and networking event of students of the Universität Hamburg and the TUHH with students and scientists from all over the world that are active in research on humanoid robots. Teams of the standard platform and Humanoid Kid Size League are invited to present their work.
